:jeva rdf:type paizo:NonPlayerCharacter ;
    rdfs:label "Джева"@ru,
                 "Jeva"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Девочка-оборотень четырнадцати лет, скрывающаяся в лесу Долины Темной Луны. Худощавая, зеленоглазая, невысокая для своего возраста. Мышино-каштановые волосы спутаны ветками и колючками, лицо испачкано темными пятнами. Спина, руки и ноги покрыты жестокими шрамами от 'лечебных процедур' Элары. После пожара в приюте скитается по долине, охотясь на жертв. Иногда спускается к детям Соколиной Лощины, заманивает одного-двух в лес 'поиграть' и затем пожирает их. При встрече с отрядом притворяется травмированной выжившей из пожара приюта, используя свой значительный навык Блефа, чтобы завоевать доверие и затем предать."@ru,
                 "A fourteen-year-old werewolf girl lurking in the woods of Darkmoon Vale. Rail-thin, green-eyed, particularly diminutive for her age. Her mouse-brown hair is a tangle of twigs and brambles and her face is smudged with dark stains. Her back, arms, and legs are covered with brutal scars from Elara's 'curative treatments.' Since she burned down the orphanage, she has skulked about Darkmoon, preying on anyone crossing her path. On occasion, she goes down among the children of Falcon's Hollow, lures one or two into the woods to 'play' and subsequently devours them. When PCs approach, she begins to stalk them in human form. If discovered, Jeva relies upon her considerable Bluff to present herself as a traumatized survivor of the orphanage fire, planning to betray and murder them all later for fun."@en ;
    paizo:hasType mm35:werewolf ;
    paizo:locatedIn hlh:darkmoon_vale ;
    paizo:hasGameStatsDnd3p5 "CR 4; Female human werewolf rogue 2; CE Medium humanoid (shapechanger); Init +8; AC 18, touch 14, flat-footed 14; hp 26 (2d8+4 and 2d6+4); Fort +5, Ref +10, Will +4; DR 5/silver; Spd 30 ft.; Melee 2 claws +3 (1d4+1) and bite -1 (1d6); Special Attacks sneak attack +1d6; SQ alternate form, wolf empathy, trapfinding, evasion; Str 12, Dex 19, Con 15, Int 12, Wis 14, Cha 15; Base Atk +2; Grp +3; Feats Improved Initiative, Iron Will, Skill Focus (Bluff), Track, Weapon Focus (bite); Skills Bluff +12, Control Shape +9, Diplomacy +8, Hide +11, Intimidate +8, Listen +6, Move Silently +11, Open Lock +8, Spot +6, Survival +6 (+10 tracking by scent), Tumble +10; Languages Common, Elven; Gear garnet ring (10 gp), tattered clothes. Human form: AC 16, touch 14, flat-footed 12; hp 18; Fort +3, Ref +8; Str 10, Dex 15, Con 11, Int 12, Wis 14, Cha 15."@en .

